title: Which Do You Prefer: Deepika Padukone’s Minimal Or Glam Beauty Look?
text:
Natasha Patel Jan . 6 . 2017 
Deepika Padukone is recently in Mexico to promote her xXx movie and I’m sure by the time she leaves, the city might be on fire—Because she’s so freakin’ HOT! Yesterday celebrity makeup artist Hung Vanngo created 2 magnificent looks that left us a little speechless. The minimal, dewy and bronzed look A photo posted by Hung Vanngo (@hungvanngo) on Jan 5, 2017 at 8:47am PST The glamorous, vixen-like look A photo posted by Hung Vanngo (@hungvanngo) on Jan 5, 2017 at 6:08pm PST 
Which one’s your fav? 2
